snippet.title: Five Nights at Treasure Island: Room Zero Demo Trailer
snippet.description: Yeah, finally made a flatscreen game! To occupy the time before my next tape I wanted to give you all something to play! So here’s this! If you wanna play the demo, click here! Have fun, dorks! https://gamejolt.com/games/RoomZero/400753
